title: Farm School NYC Graduation and Celebration 2015
desc: Join us in celebrating the graduation of Farm School NYC Students! Date:  Monday, December 8 Time:  5:30pm-8pm;  Graduation Ceremony begins at 6:30 pm Venue:  Arsenal, Central Park @ 64th Street, enter on 5th & 64th Join our 2015 Farm School NYC graduates for an end of the year celebration.? 2015 has been a busy year at Farm School NYC... we are long overdue for a celebration! ?Join us at our annual graduation ceremony. There is no admission fee!  We would appreciate any donation you could make online to help continue our mission to train urban agriculture leaders in our city.
